00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:13,350
Cik tak tahu lagi?

246
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:16,760
Baru-baru ini, Yanbei
dilanda masalah besar.

247
00:19:17,960 --> 00:19:18,790
Apa yang berlaku?

248
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:19,720
Apa sebenarnya yang berlaku,

249
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:21,480
rakyat biasa memang tak tahu.

250
00:19:21,550 --> 00:19:22,680
Namun beberapa hari ini,

251
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:24,310
banyak kota dan pekan di Yanbei

252
00:19:24,310 --> 00:19:26,200
telah diserbu oleh Tentera Helang Hitam.

253
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:27,920
Katanya mereka nak menangkap

254
00:19:27,920 --> 00:19:30,240
pemberontak daripada Persatuan Datong.

255
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:31,200
Saya dengar,

256
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:34,240
Persatuan Datong menyerang hendap
di Gunung Min Barat,

257
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,400
berniat untuk memberontak.

258
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,830
Semua orang dah dibunuh.

259
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:39,610
Adakah ini arahan daripada Maharaja Yan?

260
00:19:39,610 --> 00:19:40,350
Taklah.

261
00:19:41,270 --> 00:19:43,070
Ini arahan Panglima Cheng Yuan.

262
00:19:43,110 --> 00:19:43,960
Awak tak tahu,

263
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:45,000
baginda dah gering.

264
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:46,830
Tabib diraja pun
tak dapat merawat baginda.

265
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:48,750
Mereka sedang mencari tabib rakyat
di seluruh Yanbei untuk masuk ke istana

266
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:50,010
bagi merawat baginda.

267
00:19:51,070 --> 00:19:52,240
Jalan, cepat!

268
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,200
Jalan!

269
00:19:55,270 --> 00:19:56,000
Cepat jalan!

270
00:19:57,630 --> 00:19:58,460
Nampaknya

271
00:19:58,710 --> 00:20:01,770
seorang lagi pemberontak
daripada Persatuan Datong.

272
00:20:18,810 --> 00:20:21,000
Orang digantung macam ini,
dapat hidup lagi?

273
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,400
Apalah hidup lagi?

274
00:20:22,470 --> 00:20:23,840
Dia orang Persatuan Datong,

275
00:20:23,840 --> 00:20:25,440
mana mungkin baginya hidup?

276
00:20:25,590 --> 00:20:27,790
Semua orang Persatuan Datong dah mati.

277
00:20:27,830 --> 00:20:30,560
Kehidupan di Yanbei
akan jadi lebih susah kelak.

278
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:37,240
Saya dengar bukan saja Persatuan Datong,

279
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:39,400
malah Tentera Anggun
yang terkorban di Gerbang Meilin

280
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:41,060
juga angkara Panglima Cheng.

281
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:43,400
Lima ribu Tentera Anggun
menentang seratus ribu Tentera Yong,

282
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:44,310
dah dikorbankan.

283
00:20:44,310 --> 00:20:45,750
Mana mungkin ada yang hidup?

284
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:47,310
Mayat mereka dah
dibuang ke kubur ramai,

285
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:48,710
tiada orang yang peduli.

286
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:55,550
He Xiao.

287
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,110
Komander Chen.

288
00:21:01,270 --> 00:21:02,310
Di mana kamu?

289
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:08,400
He Xiao!

290
00:21:13,190 --> 00:21:14,670
Adakah saya tersilap?

291
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:16,310
Kamu keluar!

292
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:19,480
He Xiao, Komander Chen!

293
00:21:19,790 --> 00:21:20,790
Keluar!

294
00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:23,070
Saya mahu kamu hidup!

295
00:22:50,960 --> 00:22:52,200
Saya sudah lama jangkakan,

296
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:54,070
maharani seorang yang setia.

297
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:57,350
Walaupun terpaksa korbankan nyawa sendiri,

298
00:22:57,350 --> 00:22:59,510
awak tetap akan datang
selamatkan bekas rakan seperjuangan.

299
00:22:59,510 --> 00:23:00,110
Oleh itu,

300
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:03,510
saya sengaja tunggu awak di sini.

301
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:07,830
Saya dan Panglima Cheng juga pernah
jadi rakan seperjuangan.

302
00:23:07,830 --> 00:23:09,030
Sayangnya sekarang,

303
00:23:09,680 --> 00:23:11,140
kita terpaksa jadi musuh.

304
00:23:14,590 --> 00:23:15,310
Kejar!

305
00:23:32,790 --> 00:23:33,510
Cik Yu!

306
00:23:39,510 --> 00:23:40,270
Cik Yu!

307
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:44,590
Bertahan!

308
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:47,420
Cepat awak lari, jangan pedulikan saya!

309
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:55,760
Kita lompat ke dalam sungai!

310
00:23:59,570 --> 00:24:00,510
Bunuh mereka!

311
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:13,400
Chu Qiao,

312
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:16,640
hari inilah ajal awak.

313
00:24:44,590 --> 00:24:45,440
Cik Yu!

314
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:30,960
Chu Qiao,

315
00:25:31,790 --> 00:25:33,000
awak mesti mati.

316
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,160
Demi awak, Yan Xun

317
00:25:35,590 --> 00:25:37,590
berkali-kali mengabaikan Yanbei.

318
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:39,090
Kalau awak tak mati,

319
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,720
dendam rakyat Yanbei

320
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,510
dan dendam Yan Xun,

321
00:25:43,350 --> 00:25:45,720
takkan terbalas sampai bila-bila masa.

322
00:25:49,620 --> 00:25:50,680
Teruskan hidup!

323
00:25:55,310 --> 00:25:57,160
Zhong Yu!

324
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:18,680
Cik Yu.

325
00:27:19,350 --> 00:27:20,350
Cik Yu!

326
00:27:23,310 --> 00:27:24,350
Zhong Yu!

327
00:27:26,270 --> 00:27:27,640
Zhong Yu, awak di mana?

328
00:27:28,310 --> 00:27:29,920
Zhong Yu!

329
00:27:43,680 --> 00:27:44,240
Panglima,

330
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,590
masih belum jumpa Chu Qiao.

331
00:27:45,590 --> 00:27:47,000
Dia sekarang dah jadi orang tak berguna.,

332
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:47,920
takkan lari jauh.

333
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:49,110
Kumpulkan Tentera Helang Hitam
yang berdekatan

334
00:27:49,110 --> 00:27:51,270
untuk menggeledah semua kampung
di sepanjang lembah sungai.

335
00:27:51,270 --> 00:27:52,400
Cari dengan teliti sekali,

336
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:53,590
pastikan dapat carinya!

337
00:27:53,590 --> 00:27:54,070
Baik!

338
00:27:57,800 --> 00:28:00,040
[Waran Tangkap]

339
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:00,440
Semua datang tengok!

340
00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:01,720
Sesiapa yang pernah nampak perempuan ini,

341
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,790
cepat datang beritahu kami,

342
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:04,390
ada ganjaran besar menanti.

343
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:05,120
Tauke,

344
00:28:05,590 --> 00:28:06,850
apa yang berlaku lagi?

345
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:07,750
Awak tak tahu lagi?

346
00:28:07,750 --> 00:28:08,960
Saya baru datang dari sebelah timur.

347
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:09,890
Mereka kata

348
00:28:09,920 --> 00:28:12,350
nak menangkap pemberontak
daripada Persatuan Datong.

349
00:28:12,350 --> 00:28:13,720
Dah beberapa hari mereka menangkap,

350
00:28:13,720 --> 00:28:14,830
belum habis ditangkap lagi?

351
00:28:14,830 --> 00:28:15,920
Mana tahu?

352
00:28:16,070 --> 00:28:16,680
Tuan dan puan,

353
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,550
mi dah siap.

354
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:22,200
Dua hari lagi.

355
00:28:22,350 --> 00:28:24,210
Saya akan balik selepas dua hari.

356
00:28:28,120 --> 00:28:28,830
Ikutnya rapat-rapat.

357
00:28:28,830 --> 00:28:29,350
Baik.

358
00:28:44,070 --> 00:28:45,160
Kasihanilah saya.

359
00:28:45,510 --> 00:28:46,720
Kasihanilah saya.

360
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:47,880
Bagi saya sikit makanan.

361
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:49,110
Kasihanilah saya.

362
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,720
Semua dengar baik-baik.

363
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:51,590
Mulai hari ini,

364
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:54,240
sesiapa yang keluar
dari gerbang kota perlu diperiksa.

365
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:55,640
Harap semua bekerjasama.

366
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:57,240
Jangan cari pasal dengan saya.

367
00:28:57,240 --> 00:28:58,000
Periksa!

368
00:28:59,070 --> 00:29:00,530
Kamu tengok orang di sini.

369
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:05,110
Pernah nampak perempuan ini tak?

370
00:29:05,110 --> 00:29:06,240
Tak... tak pernah.

371
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:07,940
Pernah nampaknya?

372
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:08,720
Tak pernah.

373
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:46,270
Berhenti!

374
00:29:48,680 --> 00:29:49,880
Pusingkan muka awak.

375
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:55,830
Saya suruh awak pusingkan muka,

376
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:56,790
tak dengar?

377
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:19,450
[Li Ce, Putera Mahkota Biantang]

378
00:30:20,550 --> 00:30:22,210
Beraninya awak, si pengemis.

379
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:24,600
Awak kotorkan baju saya dan terus lari.

380
00:30:24,750 --> 00:30:26,210
Saya betul-betul malang.

381
00:30:26,270 --> 00:30:27,440
Malanglah saya datang ke

382
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:27,960
tempat terbiar

383
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:29,760
yang penuh dengan pengemis ini.

384
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:30,760
Ikut saya pergi,

385
00:30:30,760 --> 00:30:32,220
saya mesti kerjakan awak.

386
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:36,370
Tengok pakaiannya,

387
00:30:37,110 --> 00:30:38,160
orang Biantang.

388
00:30:38,550 --> 00:30:39,790
Nampak macam pondan,

389
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:41,200
badan berbau kosmetik.

390
00:30:41,200 --> 00:30:43,270
Bawa juga lencana diraja.

391
00:30:43,680 --> 00:30:44,590
Jangan-jangan dia...

392
00:30:44,590 --> 00:30:45,590
Teruskan siasat!

393
00:30:47,040 --> 00:30:48,040
Awak, berhenti!

394
00:30:48,270 --> 00:30:49,350
Si pengemis,

395
00:30:49,350 --> 00:30:50,510
awak kotorkan baju saya.

396
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:51,970
Saya pasti kerjakan awak!

397
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:53,350
Naik!

398
00:30:53,370 --> 00:30:53,810
Cepat!

399
00:30:55,120 --> 00:30:55,750
Cepatlah!

400
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:58,480
Masuk!

401
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:13,270
Qiao,

402
00:31:13,590 --> 00:31:14,510
lama tak jumpa.

403
00:31:14,790 --> 00:31:15,720
Sejujurnya,

404
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,360
perjalanan saya kali ini

405
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:19,240
berbeza dengan sebelum ini.

406
00:31:19,440 --> 00:31:21,210
Sepanjang jalan,
saya rasa segar dan bertenaga,

407
00:31:21,210 --> 00:31:22,600
ada perkara baik akan berlaku.

408
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:24,280
Saya baru saja tiba di Yanbei,

409
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:26,000
kemudian saya terjumpa awak

410
00:31:26,590 --> 00:31:27,720
antara ramai orang.

411
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:28,830
Awak rasa,

412
00:31:29,350 --> 00:31:30,310
ini dikira orang yang ada rezeki

413
00:31:30,310 --> 00:31:32,550
bertemu di tempat jauh?

414
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:34,960
Apa masalah Putera Mahkota Biantang ini?

415
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:36,230
Katanya lelaki berbau busuk,

416
00:31:36,230 --> 00:31:38,350
berkeras nak wanita cantik
yang sambut beliau.

417
00:31:38,350 --> 00:31:38,830
Ini...

418
00:31:39,350 --> 00:31:41,610
Pokok layu ini... kenapa berbunga pula?

419
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:43,310
Pokok layu berbunga,

420
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:44,310
ini petanda buruk.

421
00:31:44,310 --> 00:31:45,370
Ini petanda buruk.

422
00:31:45,680 --> 00:31:46,750
Ini malang sekali.

423
00:31:46,750 --> 00:31:47,720
Semua diam!

424
00:31:48,270 --> 00:31:50,730
Pokok layu berbunga memang jarang berlaku.

425
00:31:50,850 --> 00:31:52,980
Ia melambangkan hanya orang yang tabah

426
00:31:52,980 --> 00:31:55,700
dapat bangkit semula
dalam keadaan terdesak.

427
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:06,030
Zhao Che memang pandai uruskan hal,

428
00:32:06,030 --> 00:32:09,360
dia aturkan utusan penyambut
yang begitu comel untuk saya.

429
00:32:18,750 --> 00:32:20,480
Selamat datang, Yang Amat Mulia.

430
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:22,510
Sila ikut patik masuk ke dalam kota.

431
00:32:22,830 --> 00:32:24,070
Si cantik, awak naiklah.

432
00:32:24,070 --> 00:32:25,440
Duduk di dalam kereta kuda bersama saya,

433
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:27,300
baru saya ikut awak masuk ke kota.

434
00:32:32,590 --> 00:32:33,270
Jalan.

435
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:36,600
Yang Amat Mulia!

436
00:32:41,480 --> 00:32:43,880
Tiada kecantikan sempurna sepanjang zaman,

437
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:46,410
hanya wanita jelita
yang menyenangkan mata.

438
00:32:58,790 --> 00:32:59,640
Yang Amat Mulia!

439
00:32:59,640 --> 00:33:00,830
Berani betul awak,

440
00:33:00,830 --> 00:33:03,430
tergamak awak
pukul Putera Mahkota Biantang!

441
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:06,270
Lagi wangi.

442
00:33:07,380 --> 00:33:08,010
Chu Qiao!

443
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:09,850
Beraninya awak!

444
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:10,880
Cepat melutut!

445
00:33:12,830 --> 00:33:14,160
Kenapa awak marah-marah?

446
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:15,490
Awak tahu tak dia siapa?

447
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:17,110
Dia bakal isteri saya.

448
00:33:17,310 --> 00:33:18,830
Saya pernah jumpa ramai wanita cantik,

449
00:33:18,830 --> 00:33:20,110
tapi yang seganas dan sekejam ini,

450
00:33:20,110 --> 00:33:21,310
ini kali pertama saya jumpa.

451
00:33:21,310 --> 00:33:22,160
Si cantik, berapa umur awak tahun ini?

452
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,440
Bulan lahir bila?
Berapa ahli keluarga di rumah?

453
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:24,540
Saya berumur 21 tahun,

454
00:33:24,540 --> 00:33:25,640
dah sampai umur untuk berkahwin.

455
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:26,880
Si cantik, kahwinlah dengan saya,

456
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:27,830
jadilah pengantin saya.

457
00:33:27,830 --> 00:33:29,160
Yang Amat Mulia!

458
00:33:48,830 --> 00:33:49,550
Tabib,

459
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:51,880
bagaimana dengan kecederaan Qiao?

460
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:57,790
Tuan muda,

461
00:33:58,030 --> 00:33:59,030
pada lengan kanan

462
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:01,730
cik ini ada dua luka yang
sangat mendalam.

463
00:34:01,790 --> 00:34:04,160
Luka suku dan ketiak itu
masih boleh dirawat,

464
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:05,590
tapi luka pada lengannya

465
00:34:05,920 --> 00:34:07,350
dah menusuk uratnya.

466
00:34:08,030 --> 00:34:09,360
Biarpun disambungkan,

467
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:12,400
sama ada dia masih boleh
berlatih seni bela diri atau tidak kelak,

468
00:34:12,400 --> 00:34:13,800
sukar untuk dipastikan.

469
00:34:14,150 --> 00:34:14,949
Selain itu...

470
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:17,630
Apa itu?

471
00:34:18,510 --> 00:34:19,760
Mata cik ini

472
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:21,440
dirawat dengan terlalu lambat.

473
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,000
Takutnya

474
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:24,360
sukar untuk pulih penglihatannya.

475
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:25,960
Melainkan...

476
00:34:27,159 --> 00:34:27,960
Apa itu?

477
00:34:27,989 --> 00:34:29,400
Boleh tak habis cakap sekali gus?

478
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:31,110
Melainkan ada sejenis ubat

479
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:32,960
yang dipanggil Air Api.

480
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:33,710
Ubat apa?

481
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:35,280
Air Api.

482
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:37,800
Air Api?

483
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:39,110
Apa yang susah?

484
00:34:39,110 --> 00:34:40,150
Saya suruh orang pergi cari saja.

485
00:34:40,150 --> 00:34:40,920
Ubat ini

486
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:43,510
disediakan mengikut preskripsi
yang sangat tersulit,

487
00:34:43,510 --> 00:34:45,040
jarang ada orang yang tahu.

488
00:34:45,440 --> 00:34:46,840
Bahan-bahan perubatan
yang diperlukan untuk menyediakannya

489
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:48,100
juga sangat berharga.

490
00:34:48,110 --> 00:34:49,230
Bukan itu saja,

491
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:51,190
pesakit perlu makan ubat
selama tujuh hari,

492
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:52,070
malah setiap hari.

493
00:34:52,070 --> 00:34:54,230
mesti menggunakan ubat
yang baru disediakan.

494
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:55,960
Hentikan ubat selepas tujuh hari,

495
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:57,670
kemudian tunggu tujuh hari lagi,

496
00:34:57,670 --> 00:35:00,360
barulah matanya boleh pulih.

497
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:05,720
Terima kasih, tuan muda.

498
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:14,440
Qiao,

499
00:35:14,590 --> 00:35:15,440
jangan risau.

500
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:17,550
Tak kira air apa itu.

501
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:18,960
Biantang saya kaya dengan sumber,

502
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:19,920
apa-apa pun ada.

503
00:35:20,590 --> 00:35:21,630
Awak ikut saya balik,

504
00:35:21,630 --> 00:35:23,400
saya pasti akan sembuhkan mata awak.

505
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:24,030
Li Ce,

506
00:35:25,750 --> 00:35:27,210
awak ada nampak Zhuge Yue?

507
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:28,230
Zhuge Yue?

508
00:35:29,230 --> 00:35:30,360
Ini barang dia,

509
00:35:30,630 --> 00:35:32,090
dia yang selamatkan saya.

510
00:35:32,510 --> 00:35:33,320
Qiao!

511
00:35:34,070 --> 00:35:35,190
Awak tak berhati perut betul!

512
00:35:35,190 --> 00:35:36,710
Jelas sekali saya yang selamatkan awak,

513
00:35:36,710 --> 00:35:38,190
saya yang kutip awak dari tepi jalan

514
00:35:38,190 --> 00:35:39,230
dan bawa ke rumah tumpangan.

515
00:35:39,230 --> 00:35:41,110
Saya upah tabib untuk merawat awak.

516
00:35:41,110 --> 00:35:42,030
Awak pula

517
00:35:43,070 --> 00:35:44,880
asyik sebut nama Zhuge Yue.

518
00:35:45,150 --> 00:35:46,070
Tanpa dia,

519
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:47,960
saya dah mati di dalam tasik ais itu.

520
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:48,440
Tanpa saya

521
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:50,700
awak dah ditangkap oleh Tentera Yanbei!

522
00:35:50,820 --> 00:35:52,480
Kalau ditangkap oleh mereka,

523
00:35:52,550 --> 00:35:55,360
awak pasti menderita dan sengsara.

524
00:35:55,660 --> 00:35:57,350
Dihiris, dipotong pinggang,

525
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:59,530
dikupas kulit, ditanam hidup-hidup.

526
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:09,960
Qiao,

527
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,950
awak jangan fikir banyak-banyak.

528
00:36:11,950 --> 00:36:13,840
Yang penting perlu sembuhkan mata awak.

529
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:15,150
Yanbei sejuk dan terpencil,

530
00:36:15,150 --> 00:36:16,670
kemahiran tabib pun terhad.

531
00:36:16,670 --> 00:36:18,150
Awak ikut saya balik ke Biantang,

532
00:36:18,150 --> 00:36:20,070
saya akan upah tabib diraja
yang terbaik untuk awak.

533
00:36:20,070 --> 00:36:21,130
Saya tak nak pergi.

534
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:23,510
Kenapa?

535
00:36:23,850 --> 00:36:25,280
Saya nak tunggu Zhuge Yue di sini.

536
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:25,800
Awak...

537
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:28,600
Zhuge Yue...

538
00:36:29,590 --> 00:36:32,110
Zhuge Yue...

539
00:36:33,710 --> 00:36:34,360
Qiao,

540
00:36:34,670 --> 00:36:35,960
awak tak berubah langsung.

541
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:37,000
Awak masih

542
00:36:37,280 --> 00:36:39,610
takkan berganjak dengan keputusan awak.

543
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:40,480
Namun,

544
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:42,860
saya memang suka awak yang macam ini.

545
00:36:56,130 --> 00:36:59,390
♪ Ketawa sebab tak dapat ♪

546
00:36:59,930 --> 00:37:02,640
♪ Mengetahui kausalitas ♪

547
00:37:02,870 --> 00:37:04,640
♪ Kenapa hidup ♪

548
00:37:05,110 --> 00:37:09,200
♪ Selalu meninggalkan penyesalan
sebagai tetamu? ♪

549
00:37:10,790 --> 00:37:13,290
♪ Salju jatuh ♪

550
00:37:13,830 --> 00:37:17,390
♪ Takdir menyelaraskan ♪

551
00:37:17,650 --> 00:37:18,890
♪ Akhirnya ♪

552
00:37:19,690 --> 00:37:21,530
♪ Jatuh ♪

553
00:37:21,560 --> 00:37:23,980
♪ Sebelum subuh ♪

554
00:37:24,410 --> 00:37:26,680
♪ Sebagai pengembara di tanah asing ♪

555
00:37:26,980 --> 00:37:31,170
♪ Tak mencari
tak bertanya dan tak berkata ♪

556
00:37:31,760 --> 00:37:34,130
♪ Biar mengembara di mana-mana saja ♪

557
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:38,690
♪ Tanpa rasa kecewa
tanpa akar dan tanpa arah ♪

558
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:41,130
♪ Terkunci dalam hati ♪

559
00:37:41,380 --> 00:37:42,680
♪ Biarkan kenangan ♪

560
00:37:42,700 --> 00:37:46,390
♪ Tenggelam dalam waktu malam ♪

561
00:37:47,120 --> 00:37:48,620
♪ Lihat ♪

562
00:37:48,780 --> 00:37:52,750
♪ Alam dunia dah lupakanku ♪

563
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:55,580
♪ Harap ♪

564
00:37:56,290 --> 00:38:05,610
♪ Kau akan lupakanku ♪

565
00:38:01,590 --> 00:38:02,360
Li Ce.

566
00:38:06,670 --> 00:38:07,670
Adakah awak?

567
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:15,030
Boleh ambilkan saya air?

568
00:38:41,190 --> 00:38:42,320
Kenapa dengan awak?

569
00:39:03,030 --> 00:39:03,760
Li Ce.

570
00:39:04,480 --> 00:39:06,480
Kenapa awak banyak bercakap
pada waktu siang,

571
00:39:06,480 --> 00:39:08,710
tapi senyap saja pada waktu malam?

572
00:39:09,630 --> 00:39:10,320
Selain itu,

573
00:39:10,810 --> 00:39:13,410
kenapa awak datang
ke bilik saya tengah malam?

574
00:39:17,920 --> 00:39:18,550
Li Ce?

575
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:20,960
Li Ce?

576
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:50,840
Saya tahu awak yang datang,

577
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:51,840
Zhuge Yue.

578
00:39:51,920 --> 00:39:53,520
Awak seorang lelaki sejati,

579
00:39:53,540 --> 00:39:54,760
tapi teragak-agak dan perlahan-lahan.

580
00:39:54,760 --> 00:39:56,110
Kalau awak nak mengenalinya,

581
00:39:56,110 --> 00:39:57,110
naiklah carinya.

582
00:39:57,280 --> 00:39:58,480
Qiao bukannya bodoh.

583
00:39:58,710 --> 00:40:00,840
Dia pasti dapat rasa awak masih hidup.

584
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:02,780
Sekarang dah hari keenam,

585
00:40:03,190 --> 00:40:04,390
awak rasa macam mana?

586
00:40:05,230 --> 00:40:06,560
Siapa awak sebenarnya?

587
00:40:06,590 --> 00:40:08,520
Kenapa hantar Air Api kepada saya?

588
00:40:08,900 --> 00:40:10,290
Zhuge Yue

589
00:40:10,530 --> 00:40:11,680
dah mati.

